Calculate Growth Rate
Here we will create the growth rate.

#reshape
df_gr &lt;- df_lim |&gt; 
    mutate(pd = ifelse(year == max(year), "end", "start")) |&gt; 
    select(-year) |&gt; 
    pivot_wider(
        names_from = pd,
        values_from = tot_benes)

df_gr &lt;- df_gr |&gt; 
    mutate(
        gr_pct = (end - start) / start,
        gr_abs = end - start)
